data.description: MOVE IN READY!  LANDSCAPING AND FENCED IN YARD! 5 STALL GARAGE! 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 11' ceilings on the main floor! Primary bath with tiled walk-in shower and large walk-in closet, GORGEOUS kitchen with a large island, quartz countertops, and walk in pantry. The large DAYLIGHT BASEMENT has 9' ceilings, electric fireplace, and large bar area. The backyard has planted trees, decorative concrete patio, fire pit, iron fence, covered deck, and sits on a corner lot with beautiful tree line views!  Also the HUGE GARAGE with 5 stalls! Right around the corner from the new Robinson Elementary!! Welcome home!
